# Real Cloudflare resource IDs used by `pnpm deploy` (scripts/wrangler-render.mjs substitutes
# them into apps/*/wrangler.deploy.*). The committed wrangler.* files keep zero-UUID dummies
# that local dev (miniflare) uses unchanged. Copy this file to `.env.local`, fill in, then:
#   set -a; source .env.local; set +a
# For CI, the same names live as GitHub repo secrets — see .github/workflows/deploy.yml.
SIGMA_D1_ID=
